reviews.review_text:
only back into I think this is the only time they ever went back into/or at least tried to go back into Crazy Fingers.
The sound on this version is up there with many other great sound 82 shows.In your face sound for back then.I must say these 3 days at the rocks were wild times. This was back when word among other heads was if you don't have a ticket to the rocks you wont get in..... That was true in some sense yet I think we all got in.
